snippet.title: Best VGM 563 - Dragon Quest - The Dragonlord (Final Boss)
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1986 - https://youtu.be/EDmsNVWZIws

Symphonic Suite version here: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wMvRLHgDvn0

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

NES
Dragon Quest / Warrior (1986)
The Dragonlord (Final Boss)
Koichi Sugiyama
